{"tid":727621,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"情侶間最幸福嘅事一定係plan定下一個旅行去邊","createTime":"2018-07-03T07:15:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-04T11:38:37.000Z","uid":172607,"like":109,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"e8bced5b4a9c540434d4520d97a72319d85ba878","tid":727621,"uid":172607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T07:15:07.000Z","msg":"睇落好似好簡單嘅野<br />\n其實唔係必然<br />\n如果男女其中一方有暗湧/想分手/有第三者<br />\n其實佢地唔會願意同你搶定下年或半年後嘅機票<br />\n更加唔好講會plan行程去邊度玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為佢地唔想買完機票book哂酒店但去唔成個旅行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果你地另一半隨時都好想同你地plan定下一個旅行<br />\n甚至寫定要同你必去嘅旅遊地點<br />\n巴絲打們一定要珍惜呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afce6c102ddf9765ed13526f0adf044765782922","tid":727621,"uid":172607,"like":44,"dislike":1,"score":43,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T07:20:57.000Z","msg":"不妨試下同另一半提議下去旅行<br />\n如果佢嘅答覆係「好呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」當然無問題<br />\n<br />\n如果話「到時再算啦！」<br />\n就自己醒水啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd30bb0131f47453e4be0370f1faf96da4daed64","tid":727621,"uid":172607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T08:03:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99704f142883d270bc7b38dd1acb9f8aa3e7439b","tid":727621,"uid":172607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T08:03:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45a29a22a356da6e3c1e4e1431f5c784b44f6562","tid":727621,"uid":44333,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy